column58: A rare find! One of very few single level 4 bedroom homes located in desirable Hassler Farms subdivision! Built in 2020. Open concept kitchen, pantry, granite countertops, island seating & gas fireplace! Large primary suite with tray ceilings, dual sinks. Beautiful quartz walk in shower & large walk in closet. Covered patio plus new landscaping which includes concrete pathway to the gazebo, adorable plunge pool & fire pit. Easy to maintain river rock, fully fenced backyard, garage is equipped with 220 power

column58: Adorable home in a great location! This home is located on a private corner lot. Walking into this home you will be greeted with modern colors, an open floor plan, crown molding and wood floors. This home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, white painted cabinets, an island with raised breakfast bar and a gas stove. The living room features high ceilings, wood floors, fireplace with gas logs, lots of built-ins, and wall of windows overlooking the backyard. The master is spacious with a tray ceiling. The master bath has a double vanity, custom tile shower with a rain shower head, separate jetted tub and a walk in closet. The back porch opens onto a flag stone patio overlooking the landscaped, fully fenced yard. Enjoy the community pool which is just around the corner! This home is on the private back street and did not flood. Flood zone X. To top it off, this home has a whole house generator, is under yearly pest control, and the garage has an 8 x 12 storage room!

column58: Peace & quiet is what the owner loved living on this cul-de-sac!  4 bedroom is roomy enough for the growing family.  Enjoy entertaining on the 18 x 18 deck, right off of dining area.  Kitchen has ample cabinets/counter top space along with a breakfast bar.  Enjoy the cozy night in front of your brick fireplace in the lower level family room, with sliding doors to rear yard.  Don't worry if the power goes out, your Kohler Generator will automatically kick on and you won't loose a beat!  Newly added central A/C, radon system & water treatment system are a plus!  Two car built in garage was converted to a one car with other bay used as work area, but can be easily converted back.  20 x 24 detached 2 car garage a bonus!  Check out all this property has to offer!

column58: Lake home with a dock and privacy! Enjoy this beautiful, spacious fully furnished home towards the end of a quiet cul-de-sac. Built on almost half an acre, this level lot provides an easy stroll down to the lake and plenty of privacy. In addition to three bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, the living space includes a formal dining room, bonus room perfect for an office or playroom, and a large family room overlooking the lake. The primary suite boasts two walk-in closets and a full bath with a double vanity. A massive stone fireplace is featured in the open, eat-in kitchen.Walk outside onto your spacious back deck to enjoy the peaceful lake from your favorite chair! There?? plenty of space for three vehicles in the garage or up to a 27' boat, in addition to a flex room and bathroom, from coming in from the lake, or extra storage space. This beautiful home has a lot to offer as a primary residence, vacation home or possible STR! No HOA, no restrictions. Please call agent for showing instructions.

column58: Spacious residence perfect for a growing family! This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home is eagerly awaiting its new owners: YOU! The chef's kitchen boasts ample counter space, an open concept design, and plenty of natural light. The large master bedroom features walk-in closets, and the ensuite master bath includes a private water closet.  Secondary bedrooms offer ample space and share a centrally located hall bathroom. One of the bedrooms even features a flexible room that can be transformed into anything you desire: a playroom, music room, study, craft room??he possibilities are endless! Enjoy the convenience of a private 2-car garage and revel in the fantastic and convenient location! No HOA

column58: Welcome to this stunning custom-built 5B, 4B Central Hall Colonial in a tranquil wooded setting. This spacious home, built in 2009, sits on 10+ acres and boasts 5000 SF of living space. Upon entry, a sunlit two-story foyer showcases exquisite craftsmanship and luxury finishes. The main level features 9-ft ceilings and hardwood oak floors, leading to the FDR and LR with top-of-the-line Anderson windows and French doors. The spacious family room with a granite gas fireplace connects to the expansive mahogany deck. The chef's kitchen BOAsts granite countertops, dual center islands, and professional Thermador appliances. Custom cherry cabinetry from Vermont provides ample storage. The luxurious primary suite features a sitting room, a WIC, and a spa-like bath with a double vanity, shower, and jetted tub. Three additional spacious bedrooms share a well-appointed full bath with double vanities. Enjoy the convenience of the second-floor laundry and hookups in the basement. The spacious finished walkout basement features a rec room, a bedroom with a full bath, and plumbing for a wet bar. This home also includes 3-zone central heating and cooling, a security system, French drains, and a sump pump. Low property taxes and no flood insurance. Enjoy the best of Chatham, with access to top-rated schools, public transport, major highways, and proximity to shopping, dining, and rec activities. NYC is only 30 min away, Newark Airport is 20 min. Don't miss this remarkable opportunity!

column58: Beautifully maintained single-family home located in sought-after May?? Quarter community in Woodbridge. Built in 2020, this bright and sunny home features 4 spacious bedrooms and 4.5 bathrooms. The open-concept main floor boasts a gourmet kitchen equipped with smart appliances, quartz countertops, luxury vinyl plank flooring, access to a lovely deck, and a private office.  The lower level offers a generous family room, a den that can serve as a home theater, or potential bedroom (NTC), a full bathroom, and a walk-out to a fully fenced backyard with a shed for storage and a separately fenced side yard for added privacy. It also includes a sprinkler system for easy lawn maintenance and a 220-volt outlet in the garage for charging electric vehicles. This vibrant community offers many amenities, including a pool, clubhouse, and tennis and basketball courts.  Enjoy the fantastic location close to shops and great restaurants at Stonebridge and Potomac Mills. Nearby parks, walking and biking trails, Chinn Aquatics & Fitness Center, Prince William Ice, and Waterworks Water Park offer endless recreation options. The Occoquan and Potomac rivers provide plenty of opportunities for fishing, boating, and other water activities.   With easy access to I-66, I-95, and commuter lots, this home is also located in the Colgan High School district.  Schedule your showing today!

column58: Welcome to this stunningly renovated 3-bedroom, 4-bathroom home, where every detail has been thoughtfully considered. The spacious layout includes an additional room in the basement, perfect for use as a fourth bedroom. The oversized garage accommodates up to four vehicles, with space arranged 2 deep and 2 wide, providing exceptional convenience.  Step into the private rear yard, which features a large 20x20 storage shed, ideal for extra storage. Inside, the main floor boasts a beautiful gourmet kitchen with elegant granite countertops, flowing seamlessly into the expansive dining and living areas. A bedroom and full bathroom complete the first level. Upstairs, you'll find two generously sized bedrooms, each with its own full bathroom.  The lower level offers even more versatility with an additional full bath and another room that can serve as a fourth bedroom. This home has been freshly painted, creating a modern and inviting ambiance throughout.  Bonus features include a Bose sound system, an electric fireplace, four mounted TVs, a car lift, and an air compressor ??all of which convey with the property. Don't miss out on the comfort and style of this exceptional home ??Welcome Home!

column58: This charming brick-front, 2-car garage home in Victory Ridge is ready for its new owners!  As you enter this gorgeous home, you're greeted by formal living and dining rooms, perfect for special occasions. Adjacent to the formal dining room is a convenient bar area. The gourmet kitchen features granite countertops and a large island, perfect for casual dining. Stainless steel appliances include a double wall oven, dishwasher, electric cooktop, and a refrigerator (note: ice maker is non-functional). The kitchen is further enhanced with a stylish backsplash and extended cabinet space, providing ample storage. Just off the kitchen is the morning room, which opens directly to the backyard for easy indoor-outdoor living. The welcoming family room features a charming gas fireplace with elegant stone accents and soaring two-story ceilings. Expansive windows fill the room with natural light. The dedicated office features custom built-in bookshelves, providing the perfect space for a home library or workspace. Gleaming hardwood floors flow throughout the main level. The laundry room is situated in the mudroom off the garage, complete with a sink, washer, and dryer. A conveniently located half bath completes this well-designed main level.   The beautifully designed upper level features 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, with a hallway that overlooks the stunning two-story family room. The primary bedroom is a luxurious retreat with two large walk-in closets for ample storage and gorgeous hardwood floors that add a touch of elegance. The room also includes a mounted TV and a cozy electric fireplace, both of which convey with the home, creating the perfect space to relax and unwind. Step into the stunning en-suite bathroom, which features custom granite countertops on each vanity, a luxurious soaking tub and separate shower.  The bathroom also includes a spacious linen closet for added convenience.  One of the additional three bedrooms includes its own full bathroom and walk in closet,  providing privacy and comfort.   The expansive lower level of this home offers versatile living and entertainment spaces, perfect for gatherings and relaxation. The recreation room is a massive, flexible space that can easily be divided into two separate areas, allowing for multiple uses such as a media room, playroom, or home gym. The custom wet bar features high countertops, ample cabinet space and a built-in sink. The substantial storage area offers plenty of room to keep your belongings organized, ensuring ample space for all your storage needs. A second storage area offers even more space and can be easily transformed into a bonus room, home office, or den, depending on your needs.  A full bathroom on this level provides convenience for both guests and family. The lower level also includes walk-up stairs that lead directly to the backyard, providing easy outdoor access.   Step out into your backyard oasis that is perfect for relaxation and enjoyment. The property is completely fenced in, providing both privacy and security. The backyard features an impressive heated pool with an 8-foot depth, vinyl liner, and a sand filter system for easy maintenance. The pool also comes with a spring-loaded cover, and a robotic pool cleaner to keep the water crystal clear. All pool equipment and accessories convey with the home.  A fully automated RainBird in-ground sprinkler system services both the front and back yards, making lawn maintenance a breeze and keeping the landscaping lush and vibrant.  The thoroughly maintained yard features beautiful landscaping and a spacious 12x10 shed provides additional storage for outdoor equipment, tools, or seasonal items.   Located off Hoadly Road (next to Prince William Parkway), this property offers convenient access to shopping, restaurants, and major roads. It is zoned for Colgan High School and is in close proximity to I-95, VRE, Quantico, and Fort Belvoir, making it perfect for commuters.

column58: Welcome home! This spacious ranch home greets you with brand new LVP flooring and fresh paint throughout. Offering modern convenience, this home is equipped with Alexa integration, allowing voice control of the home's outlets, lighting and outdoor speakers. The home features a large finished basement, perfect for additional living space or entertainment. Nestled next to a public trail, you'll have direct access to a nearby public park with a pool, basketball court, and playground for kids. The expansive backyard and newly installed deck is ideal for gatherings and outdoor fun, providing plenty of space for entertaining. This tech-savvy home blends comfort and convenience in a great location with no HOA, giving you the freedom to enjoy your new home inside and out.

column58: Schedule your showing Now!! This Nokesville Charming Raised Rambler on 1.34 Acres  is a MUST SEE! It's a beautifully updated 4-bedroom, 2- full bath home offers modern living in a serene setting. Fully renovated in 2018, with all the systems replaced including the HVAC system, roof, and water heater, ensuring peace of mind for years to come. The updated kitchen features stunning granite countertops and beautiful white cabinetry, perfect for any home chef.  Fresh paint throughout and new carpet in the lower finished level create a restored, inviting atmosphere. Walk out basement leads to a patio with a conveying picnic table as well as a fire pit.  A detached 2-car garage provides extra storage or workspace, as well as an unfinished upstairs studio that could be finished for more living space. Enjoy the expansive backyard lined by trees for natural privacy, & truly escape to your own outdoor space with room to relax, entertain, and enjoy nature. This move-in ready home combines modern comfort with the true Nokesville country charm! All 4 mounted TV;s convey! Two Open Houses- Friday the 11th, from 5pm -7pm. Saturday the 12 from 12pm-2pm

column58: **OPEN  HOUSE SAT 10/12 2-4PM & SUN 10/13 2-4PM**Welcome to unparalleled luxury, privacy, and convenience in this breathtaking estate. Discover luxury living in this stunning 6 bedroom, 5 bathroom home, perfectly situated on a premium 1.39-acre flat lot in a quiet cul-de-sac, backing to acres of common area with scenic wooded views. Tucked away in the desirable Estates at Breyerton, this property offers both tranquility and convenience, just minutes from upscale shopping, dining, and commuter routes. Built by Richmond American Homes, this elegant Middleburg model boasts over 5,345 square feet of finished living space and features a 3-car side-entry garage. Designed for those who appreciate craftsmanship, the home exudes sophistication with 10' ceilings on both the main and upper levels, a three-level extension, and pride of ownership evident throughout. Step inside through the grand two-story foyer and be welcomed by the warmth of refinished hardwood floors that flow seamlessly through the living spaces. The inviting family room offers plush new carpet and a cozy gas fireplace with a marble surround, while crown molding and a coffered ceiling add a touch of elegance to the space. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring hardwood floors, upgraded cabinets, stainless steel appliances, a double wall oven, built-in microwave, granite countertop, center island, pantry, a butler's pantry and built-in desk. You'll love the modern under-cabinet lighting, beautiful backsplash, and eat-in kitchen, perfect for casual meals. For formal gatherings, the dining room boasts hardwood floors, a double tray ceiling, and elegant shadow box molding. The living room features a tray ceiling and is adjacent to the sunroom, which has a vaulted ceiling, tile floor, and an atrium door leading to the exterior. The sunroom bathes the space in natural light, offering the perfect spot to enjoy the scenic views. A full bathroom on the main level makes the flexible office space ideal for working from home, as an in-law suite, or for aging in place. The laundry room is located on the main level and includes a conveying LG washer and dryer, storage cabinets, and a laundry sink. The curved oak dual staircase leads you to the upper level, where you'll find a primary suite fit for royalty, complete with a sitting room, a coffee bar with a beverage refrigerator, new carpet and two spacious walk-in closets. The luxurious primary bath features a vaulted ceiling, dual vanities, a jetted Jacuzzi tub, ceramic tile, a private water closet, and two linen closets. Additional bedrooms include a princess suite and two spacious bedrooms all with new carpet and double closets connected by a Jack-and-Jill bathroom with a double-sink vanity. The fully finished walk-out lower level offers endless possibilities with an open recreation room, exercise room, a generously sized bedroom, an adjacent full bathroom and two storage rooms. Daylight windows and 9??ceilings make this space bright and welcoming. Outside, the large deck provided the ideal space for outdoor living. With numerous updates, including a newer hot water heater (2020), HVAC Zone 1 (2017), Zone 2 (2015), Zone 3 (Sunroom, 2007), garbage disposal (2021), dishwasher (2021), microwave (2014), and LG washer and dryer (2021), this estate is meticulously maintained and ready for you to call home.

column58: Welcome to your ideal sanctuary in this beautifully renovated home, offering an expansive 2,100 finished square feet of living space spread across two thoughtfully designed levels. As you step inside, you??e greeted by an abundance of natural light that dances off the brand-new flooring and fresh paint, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The lower level is a true entertainer's dream, featuring two spacious living areas perfect for hosting friends and family gatherings, alongside a generous fifth bedroom that can serve as a guest suite or home office. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a culinary haven equipped with charming painted cabinets, sleek Corian countertops, and modern stainless steel appliances, complemented by a spacious island that provides both functionality and style. Adjacent to the kitchen, a cozy table space invites family meals and lively conversations.  Venture to the upper level, where you??l find four beautifully updated bedrooms, each adorned with overhead lighting and designed for comfort and relaxation. The thoughtful layout ensures that everyone has their own personal space, while the enclosed sunroom off the lower level serves as the perfect retreat, allowing you to bask in the sun with a good book or enjoy your morning coffee surrounded by nature. The outdoor area is a true oasis, showcasing exceptional landscaping, fruit trees, and a dedicated garden space for those with a green thumb. The fully fenced backyard is not only private but also features an oversized shed for extra storage, along with a stunning covered pavilion that sets the stage for unforgettable outdoor entertainment. With its prime location just minutes from commuter lots, Potomac Mills Mall, Stonebridge Town Center, shopping, dining, schools, and so much more, this home perfectly balances comfort and convenience. Don?? miss your chance to claim this extraordinary property as your own!
